  "texts": [
    "Fig. 20.20Fig.",
    "Distribution of recalibration factors F, derived by KVPIPE using the parameters provided by CASU, for VIKING and VIKINGlike observations in the KiDS+KiDZ fields.",
    "Following Driver et al. (2016) and Wright et al.",
    "(2019), we applied a rejection of detectors with recalibration factors F ≥ 30.",
    "There are additional indirect selections, however, that occur for fields with large PSF sizes (see Sect. 6.4)."
  ]
}